# Get your Dropbox App Key from https://www.dropbox.com/developers/apps
# Create an app → "Scoped access" → "Full Dropbox" (or "App folder")
# Add these to OAuth2 → Redirect URIs in the Dropbox console:
#   http://localhost:5299/swipik.html   ← for Electron dev
#   https://your-deployed-url/swipik.html  ← for web production
VITE_DROPBOX_APP_KEY=your_app_key_here
